summary: You can now see toddlers running around Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
You can now see toddlers running around Skyrim adding life to the game. More NPCs are now parents. Toddlers cannot be killed or pickpocketed from. If you want the Skyrim Special Edition version go [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/1015/?]here[/url]. You should also check out [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75811/?]Teenagers[/url]. And if you play Oblivion also look at my [url=http://oblivion.nexusmods.com/mods/44097/?]Oblivion Toddlers[/url].

Requirements
Skyrim

To install just download then extract folder and drag plugin into your data folder
author: LegoManIAm94
